{
  "title": "Perfectly Sweet German Noodle Noodles",
  "description": "A sweet and chewy German noodle dish featuring celery salt and wok-hei, perfect for kids and flexitarian diets. This dish is easy to make and can be served as a main course or side dish.",
  "cuisine": "German",
  "diet": [
    "flexitarian",
    "vegetarian"
